<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 15:11:21 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国对消费金融公司提出更高的标准</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-sets-higher-bar-consumer-finance-companies-2024-03-18/</link><description>中国对消费金融公司的监管规则进行了十年来的首次修订，为在世界第二大经济体提供小额个人贷款的非银行金融企业设定了更高的门槛。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 14:57:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-sets-higher-bar-consumer-finance-companies-2024-03-18/</guid></item><item><title>埃克森美孚首席执行官表示不会试图收购赫斯</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/ceraweek-exxon-mobil-ceo-says-not-trying-acquire-hess-2024-03-18/</link><description>埃克森美孚首席执行官达伦·伍兹周一表示，在与雪佛龙的纠纷中，埃克森美孚正试图确保对赫斯公司圭亚那资产的优先购买权，而不是收购该公司本身。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 14:01:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/ceraweek-exxon-mobil-ceo-says-not-trying-acquire-hess-2024-03-18/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，美国探索在国防库存中添加更多钴</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/us-explored-adding-more-cobalt-defence-stockpiles-sources-say-2024-03-18/</link><description>三名知情人士称，美国去年考虑购买钴用于国防库存，并补充说，国防后勤局（DLA）可能会考虑在未来购买钴，尽管在最新计划中决定反对。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 13:04:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/us-explored-adding-more-cobalt-defence-stockpiles-sources-say-2024-03-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国恒大旗舰公司创始人因证券欺诈被处罚</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-regulator-ban-evergrande-chairman-entering-securities-market-life-2024-03-18/</link><description>中国恒大集团创始人许家印将被终身禁止进入证券市场，并被监管机构指控该集团的旗舰部门虚报业绩、证券欺诈和未能及时披露信息，并处以人民币 4700 万元（合 653 万美元）的罚款。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 12:59:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-regulator-ban-evergrande-chairman-entering-securities-market-life-2024-03-18/</guid></item><item><title>西方谴责普京当选，中印誓言加强关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/west-decries-putins-landslide-election-win-china-congratulates-him-2024-03-18/</link><description>西方国家政府周一一致谴责弗拉基米尔·普京(Vladimir Putin)在选举中取得压倒性胜利，称其不公平且不民主，但中国、印度和朝鲜祝贺这位俄罗斯老领导人将统治期限再延长了六年。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 11:53:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/west-decries-putins-landslide-election-win-china-congratulates-him-2024-03-18/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜领导人金正恩祝贺普京连任</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/nkorea-leader-kim-jong-un-congratulates-putin-re-election-2024-03-18/</link><description>朝鲜领导人金正恩周一祝贺俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京连任，表示平壤将与他共同努力，进一步发展双边关系。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 11:41:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/nkorea-leader-kim-jong-un-congratulates-putin-re-election-2024-03-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国抗议台湾部长在美国支持的首尔峰会上扮演的角色</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-protests-taiwan-ministers-role-seoul-summit-backed-by-us-2024-03-18/</link><description>中国周一斥责韩国台湾参加美国支持的首尔民主峰会，台湾数字部长唐奥黛在峰会上发表了未经宣布的视频致辞。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 11:09:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-protests-taiwan-ministers-role-seoul-summit-backed-by-us-2024-03-18/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国复苏萌芽提振利率和石油</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-18/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 10:09:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-18/</guid></item><item><title>路透社报道SpaceX间谍卫星后，中国军方和官方媒体猛烈抨击美国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-military-state-media-slam-us-after-reuters-report-spacex-spy-satellites-2024-03-18/</link><description>中国军方和国营媒体周日指责美国威胁全球安全，几天前路透社报道称埃隆·马斯克的 SpaceX 正在为美国情报机构建造数百颗间谍卫星。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 09:33:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-military-state-media-slam-us-after-reuters-report-spacex-spy-satellites-2024-03-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平祝贺普京获胜，两国关系有望发展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/china-congratulates-putin-election-win-says-ties-will-strengthen-2024-03-18/</link><description>据中国官方媒体报道，中国国家主席习近平周一祝贺弗拉基米尔·普京连任俄罗斯总统，并表示中国将与俄罗斯保持密切沟通，推动两国伙伴关系发展。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 09:07:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/china-congratulates-putin-election-win-says-ties-will-strengthen-2024-03-18/</guid></item><item><title>2023年更多中国人结婚，结婚率九年来首次上升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/more-chinese-tied-knot-2023-lifting-marriage-rates-first-time-nine-years-2024-03-18/</link><description>2023年，中国新婚人数较上年增长12.4%，扭转了近十年来的下降趋势，因为越来越多的年轻人因COVID-19大流行而推迟了婚礼。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 07:04:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/more-chinese-tied-knot-2023-lifting-marriage-rates-first-time-nine-years-2024-03-18/</guid></item><item><title>大使称中国考虑参加瑞士乌克兰和谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-considers-taking-part-swiss-ukraine-peace-talks-ambassador-says-2024-03-18/</link><description>亚洲国家驻伯尔尼大使周一表示，中国将考虑参加旨在结束乌克兰战争的和平会议，中立的瑞士计划在未来几个月内主办该会议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 07:03:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-considers-taking-part-swiss-ukraine-peace-talks-ambassador-says-2024-03-18/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：随着央行进入起步大门，一些中国人欢呼雀跃</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-03-18/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 05:34:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-03-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪推出新版毁灭者07混合动力车，起售价更低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-launches-new-version-destroyer-07-hybrid-lower-starting-price-2024-03-18/</link><description>路透社计算显示，中国电动汽车巨头比亚迪周一推出了新版 Destroyer 07 混合动力汽车，起售价比前代车型低 11.3%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 05:19:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-launches-new-version-destroyer-07-hybrid-lower-starting-price-2024-03-18/</guid></item><item><title>随着企业将目光投向中国以外，仓库开发商押注印度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/warehouse-developers-bet-india-companies-look-beyond-china-2024-03-18/</link><description>印度南部一个庞大的工业园区越来越难找到土地，工人们正争先恐后地为那些押注印度经济繁荣或将供应链多元化到中国以外的公司建造现代化的新仓库和工厂。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 05:16:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/warehouse-developers-bet-india-companies-look-beyond-china-2024-03-18/</guid></item></channel></rss>